| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5348 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fee83f37-6659-56db-a47b-ab59af7c8357"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
